* CSV Export (Custom): Exports race results to a user-specified CSV file.
*   When to use:    After the race to export results for external use.
*   How to use:     Double-click, enter the desired file path and name, and click OK.
*   Example:        Enter ~MyRaceResults.csv to save in the race folder.
Output Format       CSV
Destination         ?Enter file path and name (e.g., ~Results.csv)
No Page Numbers
Records Per Page    100000
List DNF
Dq Field            DNF

Select              BIB
>                   0
Field               BIB
Field               Name
Field               Sex
Field               AGE
Field               DIV
Field               City
Field               State
Field               DIVPLACE
Field               DIVTOTAL
Field               SEXPLACE
Field               SEXTOTAL
Field               PACE

Event               Finish
minus               GunStart
Time Format         H:MM:SS.01
Field Header        Gun Time

Event               Finish
minus               ChipStart
Time Format         H:MM:SS.01
Field Header        Chip Time